reviews.text:
We just completed our stay here and had the most relaxing and enjoyable experience! The hotel was very accomodating for our special meal requests and we even got an upgrade to a lovely suite!
A special thank you to the following staff:
Reception- Ms Vania and Julie;
Kitchen- Chefs Dodik, Koming and Sebastian; 
Kitchen staff-Andika, Ayu, Santi, Dewi 
And to everyone who made the extra effort to make our stay such a memorable one!
